lead_paragraph: Serena Williams' serve was broken for the first time at this year's U.S. Open. Twice, in fact. She dropped a set for the first time in the tournament, too, pushed to the brink by Simona Halep in the quarterfinals.

headline.print_headline: Pushed to Brink, Williams Edges Halep, Returns to US Open SF
